- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper specifically focuses on speech transcripts and automatic speech recognition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as neural machine translation models are a type of AI technology.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses adapting a machine learning model to improve its performance on a specific task.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may discuss the use of social networks or other information networks in collecting data for training the model.
